# BudgetSplit — iOS Budget & Split Expense App

**Final Build Spec · v3.0 · For Claude Code**

> React Native (Expo) · SQLite local · offline-first · solo v1, multi-user v2
> Developer: Prem (3+ years RN/MERN, no iOS environment set up yet)
> Target: personal use on own iPhone, sideloaded via AltStore (₹0)

-----

## 0. What this app does (one paragraph)

BudgetSplit lets a single user manage unlimited budget groups (e.g. “Personal”, “Me & GF”, “Mussoorie Trip”), track income and expenses in each, split bills among group members with item-level control, and see a global financial picture across all groups. Debt simplification reduces multi-person balances to the fewest possible payments. v1 is fully offline with no accounts. v2 adds live sync so real people on other phones can share a group.

