### 16.5 Core components (spec for Claude Code to implement)

#### `<AmountText>`

Renders any paise value as a formatted ₹ string using SpaceMono. Color varies by sign.

```tsx
// positive → colors.income, negative → colors.expense, zero → colors.textPrimary
// size prop: 'xl' | 'lg' | 'md' | 'sm' — maps to type.amountXL etc.
<AmountText paise={150050} size="lg" />  // renders "₹1,500.50" in SpaceMono
```

#### `<Card>`

Standard surface. `bgCard` background, `radius.md`, `space.md` padding, no shadow (shadows look cheap on dark backgrounds — use border instead: `border: 1px solid colors.border`).

#### `<PrimaryButton>`

Full width. `accent` background, `bg` text color (dark text on amber), `radius.md`, height 52, `type.button`.

#### `<SecondaryButton>`

Outlined. `border: 1px solid colors.border`, transparent background, `textPrimary` text.

#### `<CategoryChip>`

Small pill: category icon + name. `bgMuted` background, `textSecondary` text, `radius.pill`. Tappable.

#### `<MemberAvatar>`

Circle, 40px default (32px in compact rows). Shows initials or first letter. Color = person’s `avatar_color`. Used throughout split screens.

#### `<BalanceRow>`

One row in a settle-up list: left = from-person avatar + name, right = AmountText in accent color, center = arrow icon. Height 56px.

#### `<BudgetBar>`

Full-width progress bar. Track = `bgMuted`, fill = health color (green/amber/red). Height 4px. No rounded ends on the track — flat, ledger-like.

#### `<TransactionRow>`

Category icon circle (left) + name + note (center) + amount (right, SpaceMono). Height 64px. Swipe-left to soft-delete.

#### `<FAB>` (Floating Action Button)

Bottom-right, above tab bar. `accent` background, `+` icon in `bg` color. 56px circle. Tap → bottom sheet with: “Expense”, “Income”, “Itemized Bill”.

